&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CONSULTANT UROLOGICAL SURGEON&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Applications are invited for a full time Consultant Urologist. We are looking for applicants ideally with an interest in endo-urology/laparoscopic urology or applicants with skills that complement those of the department.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will be based at Victoria Hospital, working within a purpose-built diagnostic Urology Unit. Surgically we perform open and laparoscopic upper tract surgery, PCNL, benign open pelvic surgery along with endoscopy and functional urology/continence.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Applicants should have a broad experience of Urological Surgery and must be on the GMC Specialist Register or be within six months of eligibility for inclusion.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a full time post (10 PA) with additional PAs available subject to negotiation with the successful candidate. Applications from candidates wishing to work on a part-time basis will be considered.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
